{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884815294,"sessionID":"ses_285048959ffeBjzJQPAJZjJqRK","part":{"id":"prt_d7afbc6490014Ni4nmoFWNkCSY","messageID":"msg_d7afbb9d9001Qo4M7jg7Vdyeir","sessionID":"ses_285048959ffeBjzJQPAJZjJqRK","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_8082ab8c4b1c4c56b6605481","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Design: AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 生成 Kubernetes client 代码，用于 API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh / v1alpha1`，模块路径 `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`。该客户端库遵循 Kubernetes client-go 规范，提供 typed client、informer、lister 完整生态。\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## Architecture\n10: \n11: ### Directory Structure\n12: \n13: ```\n14: client-go/\n15: ├── clientset/\n16: │   └── versioned/\n17: │       ├── clientset.go              # Clientset 主入口\n18: │       ├── scheme/                   # 类型注册\n19: │       │   ├── register.go\n20: │       │   └── doc.go\n21: │       ├── typed/\n22: │       │   └── runtime/\n23: │       │       └── v1alpha1/\n24: │       │           ├── runtime_client.go\n25: │       │           ├── agentruntime.go\n26: │       │           ├── codeinterpreter.go\n27: │       │           ├── generated_expansion.go\n28: │       │           ├── doc.go\n29: │       │           └── fake/\n30: │       │               ├── fake_runtime_client.go\n31: │       │               ├── fake_agentruntime.go\n32: │       │               ├── fake_codeinterpreter.go\n33: │       │               └── doc.go\n34: │       └── fake/\n35: │           ├── clientset_generated.go\n36: │           ├── register.go\n37: │           └── doc.go\n38: ├── informers/\n39: │   └── externalversions/\n40: │       ├── factory.go                 # SharedInformerFactory\n41: │       ├── generic.go                 # GenericInformer 路由\n42: │       ├── runtime/\n43: │       │   ├── interface.go           # Group 接口\n44: │       │   └── v1alpha1/\n45: │       │       ├── interface.go       # Version 接口\n46: │       │       ├── agentruntime.go\n47: │       │       └── codeinterpreter.go\n48: │       └── internalinterfaces/\n49: │           └── factory_interfaces.go\n50: └── listers/\n51:     └── runtime/\n52:         └── v1alpha1/\n53:             ├── agentruntime.go\n54:             ├── codeinterpreter.go\n55:             └── expansion_generated.go\n56: ```\n57: \n58: ### Component Responsibilities\n59: \n60: | Component | Responsibility |\n61: |-----------|----------------|\n62: | Clientset | 顶层入口，管理所有 group 版本客户端，支持 Discovery 和 RuntimeV1alpha1 |\n63: | Typed Client | REST 封装，提供 CRUD + Watch + Patch 操作 |\n64: | Informer | 缓存 + 控制器模式，自动同步 Kubernetes 资源 |\n65: | Lister | 只读缓存查询，支持 namespace 级别过滤 |\n66: | Scheme | 类型序列化和反序列化注册 |\n67: | Fake Client | 测试用内存实现 |\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## API Design\n72: \n73: ### Clientset Interface\n74: \n75: ```go\n76: type Interface interface {\n77:     Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\n78:     RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n79: }\n80: ```\n81: \n82: **Constructors:**\n83: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\n84: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\n85: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\n86: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\n87: \n88: ### Typed Client: RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n92:     RESTClient() rest.Interface\n93:     AgentRuntimesGetter\n94:     CodeInterpretersGetter\n95: }\n96: ```\n97: \n98: ### AgentRuntimeInterface\n99: \n100: ```go\n101: type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n102:     Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n103:     Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n104:     UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n105:     Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n106:     DeleteCollection(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.DeleteOptions, listOpts metav1.ListOptions) error\n107:     Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n108:     List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n109:     Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n110:     Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n111:     AgentRuntimeExpansion\n112: }\n113: ```\n114: \n115: REST Resource: `agentruntimes`\n116: \n117: ### CodeInterpreterInterface\n118: \n119: 与 AgentRuntimeInterface 相同结构，类型为 `*runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter` / `CodeInterpreterList`，REST Resource: `codeinterpreters`\n120: \n121: ### Informer Factory\n122: \n123: ```go\n124: type SharedInformerFactory interface {\n125:     internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory\n126:     Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})\n127:     Shutdown()\n128:     WaitForCacheSync(stopCh <-chan struct{}) map[reflect.Type]bool\n129:     ForResource(resource schema.GroupVersionResource) (GenericInformer, error)\n130:     InformerFor(obj runtime.Object, newFunc internalinterfaces.NewInformerFunc) cache.SharedIndexInformer\n131:     Runtime() externalversionsruntime.Interface\n132: }\n133: ```\n134: \n135: **Options:**\n136: - `NewSharedInformerFactory(client, defaultResync time.Duration)`\n137: - `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options ...SharedInformerOption)`\n138: - Options: `WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n139: \n140: ### Lister\n141: \n142: ```go\n143: type AgentRuntimeLister interface {\n144:     List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n145:     AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister\n146:     AgentRuntimeListerExpansion\n147: }\n148: \n149: type AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister interface {\n150:     List(selector labels.Selector) ([]*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n151:     Get(name string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n152:     AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion\n153: }\n154: ```\n155: \n156: ---\n157: \n158: ## Code Generation\n159: \n160: ### Generation Tool\n161: \n162: 使用 `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1\n163: \n164: ### Generation Commands\n165: \n166: ```bash\n167: make gen-client\n168: # 或\n169: hack/update-codegen.sh\n170: ```\n171: \n172: ### Generation Flags\n173: \n174: - `--with-watch`: 支持 Watch 机制\n175: - Output package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n176: \n177: ### Source Reference\n178: \n179: API 类型定义源: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/` (包含 runtime/v1alpha1 类型定义)\n180: \n181: ---\n182: \n183: ## Error Handling\n184: \n185: ### Client Errors\n186: \n187: - REST 调用返回 `*meta.StatusError` 时解析为 `errors.NewStatusError`\n188: - 网络错误、超时直接传递 Go error\n189: \n190: ### Informer Errors\n191: \n192: - `WaitForCacheSync` 返回各 resource 的同步状态\n193: - 同步失败不影响其他资源，继续重试\n194: \n195: ### Retry Strategy\n196: \n197: - 使用 client-go 内置 retry 机制 (默认指数退避)\n198: - 可通过 `NewForConfigAndClient` 注入自定义 RoundTripper\n199: \n200: ---\n201: \n202: ## Testing Strategy\n203: \n204: ### Unit Tests\n205: \n206: - **Fake Client**: 使用 `clientset/versioned/fake/` 中的 fake 实现\n207:   - `NewSimpleClientset()` — 无 watch 缓存的简单实现\n208:   - `NewClientset()` — 完整实现\n209: \n210: - **Lister Tests**: 测试缓存查询、namespace 过滤、selector 匹配\n211: \n212: - **Informer Tests**: 测试事件处理、缓存同步\n213: \n214: ### Integration Tests\n215: \n216: - 启动本地 Kubernetes (kind/minikube)\n217: - 测试 CRUD 操作与真实 API server 交互\n218: \n219: ### Fake Client Usage Example\n220: \n221: ```go\n222: import (\n223:     \"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake\"\n224:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned/fake\"\n225: )\n226: \n227: clientset := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n228: ```\n229: \n230: ---\n231: \n232: ## Security Considerations\n233: \n234: ### Authentication\n235: \n236: - 支持 kubeconfig 中的所有认证方式 (Bearer Token、Certificate、OIDC)\n237: - 通过 `rest.Config` 注入自定义凭证\n238: \n239: ### Authorization\n240: \n241: - 遵循 Kubernetes RBAC，client 端不做额外授权检查\n242: \n243: ### Rate Limiting\n244: \n245: - 可通过自定义 `http.Client` 注入限流中间件\n246: \n247: ---\n248: \n249: ## Performance Optimization\n250: \n251: ### Informer Cache\n252: \n253: - 默认 in-memory 缓存，支持 CustomResyncConfig 调优\n254: - 使用 `WithNamespace` 限制缓存范围\n255: \n256: ### Lister Index\n257: \n258: - 使用 `cache.Indexer` 支持自定义索引\n259: - 默认按 namespace 索引\n260: \n261: ---\n262: \n263: ## Dependencies\n264: \n265: | Package | Version |\n266: |---------|---------|\n267: | k8s.io/client-go | v0.34.1 |\n268: | k8s.io/api | v0.34.1 |\n269: | k8s.io/apimachinery | v0.34.1 |\n270: | k8s.io/code-generator | v0.34.1 |\n271: \n272: (End of file)\n\n(End of file - total 272 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成\n\n## Overview\n\n生成 Kubernetes client 代码，用于 API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh / v1alpha1`，模块路径 `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`。该客户端库遵循 Kubernetes client-go 规范，提供 typed client、informer、lister 完整生态。\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Directory Structure\n\n```\nclient-go/\n├── clientset/\n│   └── versioned/\n│       ├── clientset.go              # Clientset 主入口\n│       ├── scheme/                   # 类型注册\n│       │   ├── register.go\n│       │   └── doc.go","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-035/design.md","time":{"start":1775884815272,"end":1775884815291}}}}
