{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884893556,"sessionID":"ses_285048959ffeBjzJQPAJZjJqRK","part":{"id":"prt_d7afc0b98001j4oZ3ve6nZjy9S","messageID":"msg_d7afbfee9001YU6sT1SnsBU7em","sessionID":"ses_285048959ffeBjzJQPAJZjJqRK","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_9ae9eb14981143f4b761f196","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Design: AR-041 — E2E 集成测试\n\n## Overview\n\n为 agentcube 项目实现端到端集成测试框架，验证 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group 下 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 两个 CRD 的完整生命周期。测试框架基于 client-go 库，使用 Kubernetes 原生测试模式，支持本地 kind 集群和远程 CI 环境。\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Directory Structure\n\n```\ntest/e2e/\n├── framework/\n│   ├── framework.go              # 测试框架主入口\n│   ├── config.go                 # kubeconfig 加载与配置\n│   ├── client.go                 # client-go 客户端初始化\n│   ├── namespace.go              # namespace 生命周期管理\n│   ├── events.go                 # 事件收集与断言\n│   └── cleanup.go                # 资源清理\n├── fixtures/\n│   ├── agentruntime.go           # AgentRuntime 测试 fixtures\n│   ├── codeinterpreter.go        # CodeInterpreter 测试 fixtures\n│   └── helpers.go                # 通用 fixture 辅助函数\n├── tests/\n│   ├── agentruntime/\n│   │   ├── crd_test.go           # AgentRuntime CRUD 测试\n│   │   ├── status_test.go        # AgentRuntime 状态更新测试\n│   │   └── watch_test.go         # AgentRuntime Watch 测试\n│   └── codeinterpreter/\n│       ├── crd_test.go           # CodeInterpreter CRUD 测试\n│       ├── status_test.go        # CodeInterpreter 状态更新测试\n│       └── watch_test.go         # CodeInterpreter Watch 测试\n├── suite_test.go                 # 测试套件入口\n├── Makefile                      # 测试构建与运行\n└── README.md                     # 测试文档\n```\n\n### Component Responsibilities\n\n| Component | Responsibility |\n|-----------|----------------|\n| framework | 测试基础设施：客户端初始化、namespace 管理、资源清理、事件断言 |\n| fixtures | 测试数据构建器：提供 valid/invalid CR 实例生成器 |\n| tests/agentruntime | AgentRuntime CRD 完整生命周期测试 |\n| tests/codeinterpreter | CodeInterpreter CRD 完整生命周期测试 |\n| suite_test.go | Ginkgo 测试套件初始化与配置 |\n\n---\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### Framework Config\n\n```go\ntype Framework struct {\n    Clientset          *kubernetes.Clientset\n    AgentcubeClientset *versioned.Clientset\n    Namespace          string\n    NamespaceLister    listersv1alpha1.NamespaceLister\n    AgentRuntimeLister listersv1alpha1.AgentRuntimeLister\n    CodeInterpreterLister listersv1alpha1.CodeInterpreterLister\n    StopCh             <-chan struct{}\n}\n\n// FrameworkOptions 配置选项\ntype FrameworkOptions struct {\n    Kubeconfig        string\n    NamespacePrefix   string\n    SkipNamespaceCleanup bool\n    DefaultTimeout    time.Duration\n}\n```\n\n### Test Fixtures\n\n#### AgentRuntime Fixture\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntimeBuilder struct {\n    obj *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime\n}\n\nfunc NewAgentRuntimeBuilder(name, namespace string) *AgentRuntimeBuilder {\n    return &AgentRuntimeBuilder{\n        obj: &runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n            ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n                Name:      name,\n                Namespace: namespace,\n            },\n            Spec: runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{},\n        },\n    }\n}\n\nfunc (b *AgentRuntimeBuilder) WithImage(image string) *AgentRuntimeBuilder {\n    b.obj.Spec.Image = image\n    return b\n}\n\nfunc (b *AgentRuntimeBuilder) WithReplicas(replicas int32) *AgentRuntimeBuilder {\n    b.obj.Spec.Replicas = &replicas\n    return b\n}\n\nfunc (b *AgentRuntimeBuilder) WithEnv(env map[string]string) *AgentRuntimeBuilder {\n    for k, v := range env {\n        b.obj.Spec.Env = append(b.obj.Spec.Env, corev1.EnvVar{Name: k, Value: v})\n    }\n    return b\n}\n\nfunc (b *AgentRuntimeBuilder) WithResourceRequest(cpu, memory resource.Quantity) *AgentRuntimeBuilder {\n    b.obj.Spec.Resources = &corev1.ResourceRequirements{\n        Requests: corev1.ResourceList{\n            corev1.ResourceCPU:    cpu,\n            corev1.ResourceMemory: memory,\n        },\n    }\n    return b\n}\n\nfunc (b *AgentRuntimeBuilder) Build() *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime {\n    return b.obj\n}\n```\n\n#### CodeInterpreter Fixture\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreterBuilder struct {\n    obj *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter\n}\n\nfunc NewCodeInterpreterBuilder(name, namespace string) *CodeInterpreterBuilder {\n    return &CodeInterpreterBuilder{\n        obj: &runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{\n            ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n                Name:      name,\n                Namespace: namespace,\n            },\n            Spec: runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterSpec{},\n        },\n    }\n}\n\nfunc (b *CodeInterpreterBuilder) WithImage(image string) *CodeInterpreterBuilder {\n    b.obj.Spec.Image = image\n    return b\n}\n\nfunc (b *CodeInterpreterBuilder) WithLanguage(lang string) *CodeInterpreterBuilder {\n    b.obj.Spec.Language = runtimev1alpha1.Language(lang)\n    return b\n}\n\nfunc (b *CodeInterpreterBuilder) WithResourceLimit(cpu, memory resource.Quantity) *CodeInterpreterBuilder {\n    b.obj.Spec.Resources = &corev1.ResourceRequirements{\n        Limits: corev1.ResourceList{\n            corev1.ResourceCPU:    cpu,\n            corev1.ResourceMemory: memory,\n        },\n    }\n    return b\n}\n\nfunc (b *CodeInterpreterBuilder) Build() *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter {\n    return b.obj\n}\n```\n\n### Test Context\n\n```go\ntype TestContext struct {\n    Framework *Framework\n    Name      string\n}\n\nfunc (f *Framework) NewTestContext(name string) *TestContext {\n    return &TestContext{\n        Framework: f,\n        Name:      name,\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### AgentRuntime API\n\n| Operation | Method | Endpoint | Description |\n|-----------|--------|----------|-------------|\n| Create | POST | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes | 创建 AgentRuntime |\n| Get | GET | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name} | 获取 AgentRuntime |\n| List | GET | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes | 列出所有 AgentRuntime |\n| Update | PUT | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name} | 更新 AgentRuntime |\n| UpdateStatus | PUT | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name}/status | 更新状态子资源 |\n| Delete | DELETE | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name} | 删除 AgentRuntime |\n| Watch | GET | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/watch/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes | 监听 AgentRuntime 变化 |\n| Patch | PATCH | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/agentruntimes/{name} | 补丁更新 |\n\n### CodeInterpreter API\n\n| Operation | Method | Endpoint | Description |\n|-----------|--------|----------|-------------|\n| Create | POST | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters | 创建 CodeInterpreter |\n| Get | GET | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters/{name} | 获取 CodeInterpreter |\n| List | GET | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters | 列出所有 CodeInterpreter |\n| Update | PUT | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters/{name} | 更新 CodeInterpreter |\n| UpdateStatus | PUT | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters/{name}/status | 更新状态子资源 |\n| Delete | DELETE | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters/{name} | 删除 CodeInterpreter |\n| Watch | GET | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/watch/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters | 监听 CodeInterpreter 变化 |\n| Patch | PATCH | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{ns}/codeinterpreters/{name} | 补丁更新 |\n\n### Expected Conditions\n\n#### AgentRuntime Conditions\n\n```go\nvar AgentRuntimeReadyCondition = metav1.Condition{\n    Type:   \"Ready\",\n    Status: metav1.ConditionTrue,\n}\n```\n\n#### CodeInterpreter Conditions\n\n```go\nvar CodeInterpreterReadyCondition = metav1.Condition{\n    Type:   \"Ready\",\n    Status: metav1.ConditionTrue,\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Test Assertion Patterns\n\n```go\n// 直接断言\nExpect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n\n// 条件断言\nExpect(agentRuntime.Status.Phase).To(Equal(runtimev1alpha1.Running))\n\n// 超时等待\nEventually(func() bool {\n    obj, err := client.Get(ctx, name, metav1.GetOptions{})\n    return err == nil && obj.Status.Phase == runtimev1alpha1.Running\n}, timeout, interval).Should(BeTrue())\n```\n\n### Error Categories\n\n| Category | Handling |\n|----------|----------|\n| NotFound | 使用 Gomega 的 `HaveOccurred()` 断言捕获 |\n| Conflict | 重试机制，带指数退避 |\n| Timeout | 使用 `Eventually` 包装，带自定义超时 |\n| Invalid | 验证错误返回的 `apierrors.IsInvalid()` |\n| AlreadyExists | 用于创建唯一资源时的预期错误 |\n\n### Cleanup on Failure\n\n```go\nvar _ = Describe(\"AgentRuntime\", func() {\n    var f *Framework\n    \n    BeforeEach(func() {\n        f = framework.NewDefaultFramework(\"agentruntime\")\n    })\n    \n    AfterEach(func() {\n        if CurrentGinkgoTestDescription().Failed {\n            f.DumpEvents()\n        }\n        f.Cleanup()\n    })\n    \n    It(\"should create and delete\", func() {\n        // test code\n    })\n})\n```\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Test Categories\n\n#### 1. CRUD Tests\n\n- **Create**: 验证资源创建成功，字段正确设置\n- **Read**: 验证 Get/List 操作返回正确数据\n- **Update**: 验证 spec 更新生效\n- **Delete**: 验证资源删除，级联清理\n\n#### 2. Status Update Tests\n\n- 验证 status 子资源更新\n- 验证 conditions 更新\n- 验证 phase 转换\n\n#### 3. Watch Tests\n\n- 验证资源事件触发 (Added/Modified/Deleted)\n- 验证 informer 缓存同步\n\n#### 4. Field Validation Tests\n\n- 必填字段缺失\n- 非法字段值\n- 字段格式验证\n\n### Test Execution Modes\n\n#### Local Development\n\n```bash\n# 使用 kind 集群\nmake e2e-test-local\n# 或\nE2E_KIND_CLUSTER=agentcube-e2e go test -v ./test/e2e/...\n```\n\n#### CI/CD Pipeline\n\n```bash\n# 使用 CI 配置\nmake e2e-test-ci\n# 或\nE2E_KUBECONFIG=/path/to/kubeconfig go test -v ./test/e2e/...\n```\n\n### Test Configuration\n\n```yaml\n# e2e-config.yaml\ne2e:\n  kubeconfig: \"\"\n  kind_cluster: \"agentcube-e2e\"\n  namespace_prefix: \"agentcube-e2e\"\n  timeout: 5m\n  retry_interval: 1s\n  cleanup_on_exit: true\n  \nkubernetes:\n  version: \"1.28\"\n  \nresources:\n  agentruntime:\n    default_image: \"agentcube/agent-runtime:latest\"\n    default_replicas: 1\n  codeinterpreter:\n    default_image: \"agentcube/code-interpreter:latest\"\n    default_language: \"python\"\n```\n\n### Ginkgo Test Structure\n\n```go\nvar _ = Describe(\"AgentRuntime E2E\", func() {\n    var f *framework.Framework\n    \n    BeforeEach(func() {\n        f = framework.NewDefaultFramework(\"agentruntime\")\n    })\n    \n    Describe(\"CRUD Operations\", func() {\n        It(\"should create an AgentRuntime\", func() {\n            // Create\n            obj := fixtures.NewAgentRuntimeBuilder(\"test-ar\", f.Namespace).\n                WithImage(\"nginx:latest\").\n                Build()\n            \n            created, err := f.AgentcubeClientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().\n                AgentRuntimes(f.Namespace).Create(ctx, obj, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n            Expect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n            Expect(created.Name).To(Equal(\"test-ar\"))\n            \n            // Get\n            fetched, err := f.AgentcubeClientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().\n                AgentRuntimes(f.Namespace).Get(ctx, \"test-ar\", metav1.GetOptions{})\n            Expect(err).NotTo(HaveOccurred())\n            Expect(fetched.Spec.Image).To(Equal(\"nginx:latest\"))\n        })\n        \n        It(\"should update an AgentRuntime\", func() {\n            // Update logic\n        })\n        \n        It(\"should delete an AgentRuntime\", func() {\n            // Delete logic\n        })\n    })\n})\n```\n\n### Performance Considerations\n\n- **并行测试**: 使用 Ginkgo 的 `--focus` 和 `--skip` 标签隔离\n- **资源复用**: namespace 级别 fixture，复用 informer\n- **超时控制**: 每个操作设置合理的超时，避免无限等待\n- **日志级别**: INFO 级别生产环境，DEBUG 级别调试\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version |\n|---------|---------|\n| github.com/onsi/ginkgo/v2 | ^2.14.0 |\n| github.com/onsi/gomega | ^1.28.0 |\n| github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go | latest |\n| k8s.io/client-go | v0.34.1 |\n| k8s.io/api | v0.34.1 |\n| k8s.io/apimachinery | v0.34.1 |\n\n---\n\n## CI Integration\n\n### GitHub Actions\n\n```yaml\nname: E2E Tests\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n  pull_request:\n    branches: [main]\n\njobs:\n  e2e:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - name: Setup Kind\n        uses: banzaicloud/kind-action@v1.8.0\n        with:\n          cluster_name: agentcube-e2e\n      - name: Run E2E Tests\n        run: make e2e-test-ci\n        env:\n          E2E_KUBECONFIG: ${{ env.KUBECONFIG }}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n- **Namespace 隔离**: 每个测试使用独立 namespace，避免污染\n- **资源清理**: AfterEach 确保资源清理，防止泄漏\n- **RBAC**: 确保测试 ServiceAccount 有所需权限\n- **敏感数据**: 测试 fixture 不包含真实凭据或密钥\n\n---\n\n## Future Enhancements\n\n- **Chaos Testing**: 注入故障，验证系统韧性\n- **Performance Benchmarks**: 资源创建/更新延迟基准测试\n- **Multi-cluster Tests**: 跨集群资源同步测试\n- **Upgrade Tests**: 版本升级兼容性测试","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-041/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-041/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-041/design.md","time":{"start":1775884893541,"end":1775884893552}}}}
